{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775869043201,"sessionID":"ses_285f5acf8ffek1l1CTQ0sUQCKO","part":{"id":"prt_d7a0a9ed6001YzEQPLJ5MCUtEl","messageID":"msg_d7a0a920b001AN7zwmivaqRlFG","sessionID":"ses_285f5acf8ffek1l1CTQ0sUQCKO","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_0053df7516b14555ad9b25b8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-028 — SDK AgentRuntimeClient Tasks\n\n**Module:** sdk-python  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-1 (Draft)\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Tasks\n\n### Phase 1: AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient (T001-T010)\n\n- [ ] **T001** Implement `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` class with constructor\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* Accepts `session_id`, `router_url`, `namespace`, `cr_name`, `base_url`, `timeout=120`, `connect_timeout=5.0`, `pool_connections=10`, `pool_maxsize=10`\n  - *Test:* Instantiate client, verify default values\n\n- [ ] **T002** Implement base URL construction from router components\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* When `base_url` not provided, constructs `urljoin(router_url, \"/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/agent-runtimes/{cr_name}/invocations/\")`\n  - *Test:* Verify correct URL format\n\n- [ ] **T003** Implement `_request()` helper with session header\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* Adds `x-agentcube-session-id: {session_id}` header to all requests\n  - *Test:* Make request, verify header present\n\n- [ ] **T004** Implement `execute_tool(tool_name, parameters, timeout)` via data plane\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* POSTs to `api/execute` with JSON body containing tool_name, parameters, timeout\n  - *Test:* Execute tool, verify request format\n\n- [ ] **T005** Implement `list_tools()` via data plane\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* GET `api/tools`, returns list of available tools\n  - *Test:* List tools, verify response parsing\n\n- [ ] **T006** Implement `get_tool_schema(tool_name)` via data plane\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* GET `api/tools/{tool_name}/schema`, returns tool schema\n  - *Test:* Get schema, verify response\n\n- [ ] **T007** Implement `upload_file(local_path, remote_path)` via data plane\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* POST multipart form data to `api/files` with `x-agentcube-session-id` header\n  - *Test:* Upload file, verify multipart request\n\n- [ ] **T008** Implement `download_file(remote_path, local_path)` via data plane\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* GET `api/files/{clean_path}` with `stream=True`, writes to local path\n  - *Test:* Download file, verify stream handling\n\n- [ ] **T009** Implement `list_files(path=\".\")` via data plane\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* GET `api/files` with query parameter `path`\n  - *Test:* List files, verify query param\n\n- [ ] **T010** Implement `close()` method\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* Closes HTTP session\n  - *Test:* Verify session is closed\n\n---\n\n### Phase 2: AgentRuntimeClient (T011-T020)\n\n- [ ] **T011** Implement `AgentRuntimeClient` class with constructor\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/agent_runtime.py`\n  - *Verify:* Accepts `name=\"my-agent\"`, `namespace=\"default\"`, `ttl=3600`, `workload_manager_url`, `router_url`, `auth_token`, `verbose=False`, `session_id=None`\n  - *Test:* Instantiate client, verify defaults\n\n- [ ] **T012** Implement router URL validation\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/agent_runtime.py`\n  - *Verify:* Raises `ValueError` if neither `router_url` argument nor `ROUTER_URL` env var is set\n  - *Test:* Instantiate without router_url, verify ValueError raised\n\n- [ ] **T013** Implement `_init_data_plane()` and session creation\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/agent_runtime.py`\n  - *Verify:* If no `session_id` provided, calls `cp_client.create_session()`, then initializes data plane client\n  - *Test:* Instantiate without session_id, verify create_session called\n\n- [ ] **T014** Implement data plane init failure handling\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/agent_runtime.py`\n  - *Verify:* If `_init_data_plane()` fails after session created, logs warning, deletes session, sets session_id to None, re-raises\n  - *Test:* Simulate failure, verify cleanup\n\n- [ ] **T015** Implement context manager protocol (`__enter__`, `__exit__`)\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/agent_runtime.py`\n  - *Verify:* `__exit__` calls `stop()`, which closes data plane and deletes control plane session if it was created by this client\n  - *Test:* Use client as context manager, verify cleanup on exit\n\n- [ ] **T016** Implement `execute_tool(tool_name, parameters, timeout)`\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/agent_runtime.py`\n  - *Verify:* Delegates to data plane client, returns execution result\n  - *Test:* Execute tool, verify result\n\n- [ ] **T017** Implement `list_tools()` and `get_tool_schema(tool_name)`\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/agent_runtime.py`\n  - *Verify:* Delegate to data plane client methods\n  - *Test:* List tools and get schema\n\n- [ ] **T018** Implement file operations (`upload_file`, `download_file`, `list_files`)\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/agent_runtime.py`\n  - *Verify:* Delegate to data plane client methods\n  - *Test:* Each operation works correctly\n\n- [ ] **T019** Implement `stop()` method\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/agent_runtime.py`\n  - *Verify:* Closes data plane session, deletes control plane session if created by this client\n  - *Test:* Call stop, verify cleanup\n\n- [ ] **T020** Update `agentcube/__init__.py` with AgentRuntimeClient exports\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/__init__.py`\n  - *Verify:* `AgentRuntimeClient` is properly exported\n  - *Test:* `from agentcube import AgentRuntimeClient`\n\n---\n\n### Phase 3: Tests & Examples (T021-T024)\n\n- [ ] **T021** Write unit tests for AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* All operations make correct HTTP requests\n\n- [ ] **T022** Write unit tests for AgentRuntimeClient\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/tests/test_agent_runtime_client.py`\n  - *Verify:* Full lifecycle, context manager, error handling\n\n- [ ] **T023** Create example usage script for AgentRuntimeClient\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/examples/agent_runtime_example.py`\n  - *Verify:* Demonstrates AgentRuntimeClient usage\n\n- [ ] **T024** Verify full package exports\n  - *File:* `sdk-python/agentcube/__init__.py`, `sdk-python/agentcube/clients/__init__.py`\n  - *Verify:* All clients properly exported\n  - *Test:* `from agentcube import AgentRuntimeClient; from agentcube.clients import AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient`\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Task | Depends On |\n|------|------------|\n| T002 | T001 |\n| T003 | T001 |\n| T004 | T002, T003 |\n| T005 | T002, T003 |\n| T006 | T002, T003 |\n| T007 | T002, T003 |\n| T008 | T002, T003 |\n| T009 | T002, T003 |\n| T010 | T001 |\n| T011 | AR-027 T001-T003 |\n| T012 | T011 |\n| T013 | T001, T011 |\n| T014 | T013 |\n| T015 | T013, T019 |\n| T016 | T013 |\n| T017 | T013 |\n| T018 | T013 |\n| T019 | T010, (AR-027 T007) |\n| T020 | T011 |\n| T021 | T001-T010 |\n| T022 | T011-T019 |\n| T023 | T011-T019 |\n| T024 | T020 |\n\n---\n\n## Verification Checklist\n\n- [ ] AC001: AgentRuntimeClient constructs with proper defaults (name, namespace, ttl, verbose)\n- [ ] AC002: AgentRuntimeClient creates session via ControlPlaneClient when session_id not provided\n- [ ] AC003: AgentRuntimeClient supports context manager protocol with proper cleanup\n- [ ] AC004: AgentRuntimeClient handles data plane init failure with session cleanup\n- [ ] AC005: AgentRuntimeClient raises ValueError when router_url is missing\n- [ ] AC006: execute_tool sends correct request to data plane\n- [ ] AC007: list_tools returns available tools from data plane\n- [ ] AC008: get_tool_schema returns schema for specified tool\n- [ ] AC009: upload_file uploads files via multipart to data plane\n- [ ] AC010: download_file downloads files as streams to local path\n- [ ] AC011: list_files returns file listing from data plane\n- [ ] AC012: stop closes data plane and deletes control plane session\n- [ ] AC013: Session header x-agentcube-session-id is set on all data plane requests\n- [ ] AC014: AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient constructs base_url from router components\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Delta Spec: `changes/AR-028/delta-spec.md`\n- Stub Implementation: `changes/AR-027` (Phase 6: AgentRuntimeClient Stub)\n- Base Design: `python-sdk/design.md`\n- Control Plane API: `workload-manager/api.md`","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-028/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-028/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-028/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775869043190,"end":1775869043198}}}}
